{"id": "1497466248680702012", "channel_id": "1497466248680702012", "type": 0, "author_id": "505216676430741514", "author_name": "egg1108", "author_bot": false, "content": "以下是有的角色與命輪\n想請問\n1.目前有5個自選普池命輪，原本抽巨人是想給淡墨，但突然抽封了把阿拉抽滿，需要用時間原點把巨人換成螺旋在自選滿+12給阿拉用嗎?\n\n2.目前資源應該還夠抽周年的淡墨跟合作\n想請問融災隊伍該如何組成?目標先訂在350~375\n由於經驗罐很缺，所以想請大老幫組隊伍，不然我看每隻很像都很好用，就一直分散餵\n\n目前應該\n地瓜汀克斯小騎士奧爾拉\n阿拉詹金艾爾瓦艾瑞卡\n神國隊(等半周年抽\n末夏(借角色.常常看到人說帶垃圾去自爆，大概是帶那些角色呢?\n剩下的隊伍不知道該如何組成\n\n3.看視頻常常會說銀鑰位生存位死抗位 我要如何知道哪隻是什麼位置呢?\n4.沉澱商店的阿庫特之春.隕日.靈魂誕生都先買到3疊就好?優先順序為何呢?\n\n再麻煩大佬們，謝謝", "timestamp": "2026-04-25T05:16:15.263000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1497466249096200222", "filename": "1.PNG", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 846615, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1497466248680702012/1497466249096200222/1.PNG?ex=69ed9f9f&is=69ec4e1f&hm=6c7e7aae07641f28d0a5095a425a0fcd1abaf6f7e173030d48afd3a85e4d9107&"}, {"id": "1497466249796653146", "filename": "2.PNG", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 797476, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1497466248680702012/1497466249796653146/2.PNG?ex=69ed9f9f&is=69ec4e1f&hm=9e275aee3ec0704b23d97500d48ea1d3eae10c6f5904a5cbd1297b9988abe5d8&"}, {"id": "1497466250207432849", "filename": "3.PNG", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 808287, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1497466248680702012/1497466250207432849/3.PNG?ex=69ed9f9f&is=69ec4e1f&hm=a822423c79fb2e53b7c74a3fbd4fadf677aa84512667900c2d45ee72001b680b&"}, {"id": "1497466250790567946", "filename": "4.PNG", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 577060, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1497466248680702012/1497466250790567946/4.PNG?ex=69ed9f9f&is=69ec4e1f&hm=5ab36eaa63b49a94e16dd74d44631d1ae6ba423cc9788117443c048bed4b92b9&"}, {"id": "1497466251289563187", "filename": "5.PNG", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1017657, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1497466248680702012/1497466251289563187/5.PNG?ex